Description_lang: Sylvanas launches a terror-infused arrow at a player, inflicting $358708s1 Shadow damage and additionally inflicting up to $358709s2 Shadow damage to all other players, decreasing in damage based on distance from the point of impact.Upon impact, summons $358706s1 Dark Sentinels nearby. Each time $@spellname358704 completes, Sylvanas gains $@spellname358724, increasing the number of Dark Sentinels summoned. This effect stacks.
